2-3-74 showed how one essence, one real world, can have plural, but not clashing, sets of attributes; I saw it. Here + now was Acts. But also (this is terribly, terribly vital!) also USA 1974. Acts AD 45 did not replace USA 1974; it was not here instead. This is impossible. But if it can be done with USA 1974 it can be done -can be so- with any set of space-time accidents. Any century + any place. + I have what the AI voice said: "He causes things to look different". Not change; "look different"; that's another matter. + for what purpose? "So it's appear time has passed". + why? To withhold the return of Christ from us. But Christ is here: i.e. Valis. He has invaded our enchanted world with its time dilation. The years -decades- of thinking, analysis, epistemology that produced my 10 volume meta novel would explain the "why me?". One need only consider "Eye" or "Maze" or -My God!- "Stigmata"!! + the Varley story (+ my Playboy story, as Russ pointed out - God. I never even thought about it, nor, really, the other earlier stories: "Precious Artifact", "Retreat Syndrome" etc.


